    "asOf": "2018-04-19",
    "date": "2019-08-28T15:08:00Z",
    "text": "Protecting Moms and Infants Act\n\nThis bill reauthorizes through FY2023 the residential substance-use-treatment program\u00a0for pregnant and postpartum women and requires the Department of Health and Human Services to make recommendations\u00a0for addressing prenatal opioid use. Further, the Center for Substance Abuse Treatment must develop substance-use-disorder educational materials for treating pregnant women and babies."
